name: Nicole Malachowski
description: I would rather describe myself as a straight forward person,family oriented and God fearing.I am a humanitarian who strongly believe in right to live.As a military,i see myself as the voice of the voiceless.I like meeting people and making new friends. I admire leadership qualities in others, integrity, and a way to enjoy life and look at the beauty there is. Someone who’s not afraid to try new things or even to just sit silent and appreciate the old things we have.
